{"tid":1832026,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家仲記唔記得只要死纏721呢粒核彈，呢場運動就一定唔會完？","createTime":"2020-01-21T01:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T12:06:42.000Z","uid":36592,"like":70,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0e51ee53750e4d8485005f89c21ac392b2d26efa","tid":1832026,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:16:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20191018/20788828/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191018%2F20788828%2F&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6uIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=c86e1e67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191018%2F20788828%2F&h=794f819e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20191018/20788828/</a><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗出席電台節目，鄭重呼籲大眾向前走，「不要再糾纏7&middot;21事件」，簡直是對港人的當頭棒喝。近日幾乎全港市民，都心無旁騖為十五歲小妹妹鳴冤，誰有閒情逸致「糾纏7&middot;21事件」？連8&middot;31的CCTV也被拋諸腦後了，遑論先秦時代的7&middot;21呢？在這個資訊疲勞的世界，建宗BB這句話猶如暮鼓晨鐘，發人深省。<br />\n<br />\n八月中旬，拙欄引述一位政界友人的話，提醒大家必須對7&middot;21窮追猛打，因為這是政府的死穴，坦蕩蕩暴露人前，吟詩都吟唔甩。當時他已斷言，林鄭拆不到7&middot;21，只能採取拖延戰術，讓暴力蔓延，繼而抹黑示威者，企圖逆風翻盤。事隔兩月，友人披露的政府「劇本」已逐一應驗。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抽離一點觀察，7&middot;21直到今時今日，依然是政府最大死穴。8&middot;31你沒有CCTV，根本沒法指控警方殺人──我沒忘記那位嘔白泡的男子，但誰知道他的下落呢？──至於近日接二連三的浮屍，即使可疑，大家仍然提不出證據。無憑無據的指控，不管如何群情洶湧，警方俱可置之不理，最後不了了之。<br />\n<br />\n7&middot;21恐襲則不同。它不是都市傳說，警方包庇罪犯，有圖有片有真相，這是連撐警藍屍也無法否認的事實。例如襲擊立場姐姐的男人，姓名面貌職業地址一應俱全，拘捕了沒有？為什麼不？你問盧偉聰、李家超、林鄭月娥，他們只能啞口無言。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n曾在網上看過一張照片，有抗爭者在地上塗鴉，寫了一句拉丁文：&quot;Quis custodiet ipsos custodes?&quot; 中譯是：看守者將由誰看守？我們當然明白，這是批評「香港警察，知法犯法」，但原文則另有所指。此話出自尤維納利斯的諷刺詩，「看守者」（custodes）其實是古羅馬丈夫為防帽事，派去看守妻子的人，通常由年長男士擔任（有時妻子也會反過來派人看管丈夫，如詩人馬提亞爾嘲諷過的惡妻Polla）。Quis custodiet ipsos custodes?這個修辭式提問，今天終於有答案了：張建宗。他叫你不要糾纏，聰明的你該明白怎樣做吧。"},{"pid":"4561e6d5dffd9b216ec71ee24533e32ac50a4d6e","tid":1832026,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b36f8bfc3054ac27a15acd25d36ac67aeb6a30","tid":1832026,"uid":212897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:24:53.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"6b3da3fbe1b8926b3d0a63e812368861e9faef4a","tid":1832026,"uid":117282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:33:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8f2f7b96de2819297435b8cc7a52c8911bddc45","tid":1832026,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7104b757574a88117048fb913135f680642b05","tid":1832026,"uid":224147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e51ee53750e4d8485005f89c21ac392b2d26efa","tid":1832026,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:16:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20191018/20788828/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191018%2F20788828%2F&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6uIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=c86e1e67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191018%2F20788828%2F&h=794f819e\" target=\"_